城市大學之學生電郵用作申請會員帳號。在此呼籲已使用香港城市大學電郵用作註冊之會員，前往「帳號設定」設置一個安全的「後備電郵」，並可考慮開啟「雙重驗証」（ 詳見：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2049698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2049698</a> ）以提高帳號安全性，防止當學校電郵帳號被入侵後被用作盜取討論區會員帳號。並建議學生電郵帳號避免使用入學時的預設密碼。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，管理團隊一直都有執行各種措施，例如限制部份 ISP 或學生電郵域名用作註冊，或需要進一步配合証明文件才能註冊，以防止上述之問題；一經發現會員開設分身帳號亦會立即封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n我們相當重視本次的事件，如各位發現其他會員有可疑活動，請立即向管理團隊舉報。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:02:30.000Z","msg":"wow，八大都要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8de4ba62017c3569e0b743cdcbb66daddb7f6a","tid":2326200,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:03:59.000Z","msg":"詳見：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aCeKJCV\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aCeKJCV</a><br />\n<br />\n無法顯示本主題，原因可能為：<br />\n・ 本主題不存在或已經失效<br />\n・ 你沒有權限顯示本主題"},{"pid":"8498a2e2d291803c205859e25eca24295a2e7a4d","tid":2326200,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9c822f68510ae35117bca0867d5b6bc97391eedc","tid":2326200,"uid":23575,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:01:17.000Z","msg":"點睇自己講左咩野架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:04:10.000Z","msg":"係GOOGLE起自己<br />\n一時間唔記得左點search<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你搵搵老鳳post"},{"pid":"30b2fc51c81b6ee7ba6aa561fad5768087411d4b","tid":2326200,"uid":28641,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:04:18.000Z","msg":"Shitty仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f0dea6d3ecf0e835b0fd0f78bdfcbbea645e32","tid":2326200,"uid":54195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adb279b83f7862f500c03da2b819aca4b3343b7","tid":2326200,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:04:33.000Z",